I would believe in this, but I would never relate it to God or anything. I would relate it closer to the human soul and our spiritual instinct.<br>
<br>
As for hearing your Grandma talk to you after she died, I just don't know. I wouldn't like this one bit. It wouldn't comfort me, but I would find it more spooky. I don't believe anything would ever happen, except again when a person is in such a mental state that they comfort themselves with imaginery voices and images. Without insulting you, I just don't think I could be like you.<br>
